tensions erupted into
street battles today between
police and protesters

02:36.933 --> 02:38.866 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
in Jerusalem and the West Bank.

02:38.866 --> 02:43.866 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
