killed, and nearly 400 hurt.

02:45.833 --> 02:48.866 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Exploding stun grenades
drowned out Friday prayers in
Jerusalem, as ambulance sirens

02:48.866 --> 02:51.033 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
wailed.

02:51.033 --> 02:55.366 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
