both Muslims and Jews.

02:58.400 --> 03:01.833 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
MAN (through translator):
This place is made
for worshipping God.

03:01.833 --> 03:04.433 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
