03:06.433 --> 03:09.200 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
HARI SREENIVASAN: The Israelis
put up the metal detectors
after Arab-Israeli gunmen

03:09.200 --> 03:12.000 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
killed two police
officers last Friday.

03:12.000 --> 03:17.000 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
