third holiest site in Islam, and
the Dome of the Rock, they're

03:22.333 --> 03:26.200 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
bordered by the Western Wall,
the holiest site in Judaism.

03:26.200 --> 03:29.200 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
Tensions have been building
ever since the shooting.

03:29.200 --> 03:33.533 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Overnight, the streets of
Jerusalem's Old City were
filled with protesters throwing

03:33.533 --> 03:37.233 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
