04:19.266 --> 04:22.966 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
HARI SREENIVASAN: The violence
broke out after prayers, and
spilled over to towns across

04:22.966 --> 04:25.500 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
the West Bank.

04:25.500 --> 04:29.033 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Later, the day of rage
turned to grief, as
mourners held a funeral
for one of the Palestinian

04:29.500 --> 04:31.600 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
dead.

04:31.600 --> 04:34.300 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
