05:27.066 --> 05:31.666 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
HARI SREENIVASAN: Meanwhile,
Qatar's emir denounced the
blockade as a smear campaign,

05:32.533 --> 05:34.533 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
