and the tremor caused heavy
damage to buildings, roads and

06:06.333 --> 06:07.866 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
historical sites.

06:07.866 --> 06:10.000 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
