but got stranded.

06:12.833 --> 06:17.800 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
WOMAN (through translator):
We were woken up at
1:30 in the morning.

06:17.800 --> 06:19.633 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
We were wondering what happened.

06:19.633 --> 06:20.866 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
