and lamps were upside down.

06:36.666 --> 06:40.800 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
HARI SREENIVASAN: The two
people killed were identified as
tourists from Turkey and Sweden.

06:40.800 --> 06:45.233 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
