the counter of a specialty
foods store, trying to figure

45:28.433 --> 45:30.366 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
it out.

45:30.366 --> 45:32.400 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
WILLIAM BRANGHAM: The
store she bought was called
the Barefoot Contessa.

45:32.400 --> 45:35.800 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
That was the nickname
of the prior owner.

45:35.800 --> 45:40.800 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
It was 1978, and this
was Garten's very first
job in the food industry.

45:41.666 --> 45:42.566 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
So, had you been a cook before?

45:42.566 --> 45:43.566 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
INA GARTEN: No.

45:43.566 --> 45:44.766 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
WILLIAM BRANGHAM: Not at all?

45:44.766 --> 45:45.800 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
INA GARTEN: I'd never
worked in a store.

45:45.800 --> 45:47.466 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
I never worked in a restaurant.

45:47.466 --> 45:50.000 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
