45:55.000 --> 45:57.166 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
WILLIAM BRANGHAM: And you have
had no training beyond that?

45:57.166 --> 45:58.166 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
INA GARTEN: No.

45:58.166 --> 45:59.400 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
No.

45:59.400 --> 46:00.266 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
WILLIAM BRANGHAM:
That's amazing.

46:00.266 --> 46:02.366 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
INA GARTEN: Thank you.

