46:32.700 --> 46:36.400 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
And then you would look at the
recipe and say, I can actually
make that and I can make

46:36.400 --> 46:38.666 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
it with ingredients I can
find in the grocery store.

46:38.666 --> 46:40.633 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
I don't think that's
changed at all.

46:40.633 --> 46:44.333 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
WILLIAM BRANGHAM: Having taught
yourself how to cook, does
that inform the recipes that

46:44.333 --> 46:47.866 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
