from a professionally trained

46:47.866 --> 46:50.633 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
mind, but someone who
did this on her own?

46:50.633 --> 46:52.766 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
INA GARTEN: That's really smart.

46:52.766 --> 46:54.866 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Actually, when I first started
writing cookbooks, I remember
thinking to myself, what makes

46:54.866 --> 46:56.333 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
