46:58.566 --> 47:03.566 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
And, as I started, I realized,
actually, what is my lack is
actually exactly right, because

47:06.266 --> 47:08.800 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
I can connect with --
cooking's hard for me.

47:08.800 --> 47:09.966 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
I never worked on...

47:09.966 --> 47:11.200 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
WILLIAM BRANGHAM:
Cooking is hard for you?

47:11.200 --> 47:13.133 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
INA GARTEN: It is
so hard for me.

47:13.133 --> 47:14.766 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
Anybody that works
with me will tell you.

47:14.766 --> 47:16.866 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
It's so hard for me.

47:16.866 --> 47:21.233 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
And that's why my recipes
are really simple, because I
want to be able to do them.

47:23.200 --> 47:26.466 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
WILLIAM BRANGHAM: Soon,
executives at the Food Network
came calling, and calling, and

47:30.866 --> 47:32.300 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
