47:35.933 --> 47:37.400 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
WILLIAM BRANGHAM: Really?

47:37.400 --> 47:40.033 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
INA GARTEN: I just said no
over and over and over again.

47:40.033 --> 47:41.533 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
WILLIAM BRANGHAM: Why?

47:41.533 --> 47:43.000 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
INA GARTEN: I just didn't
think I'd be good on TV.

47:43.000 --> 47:45.766 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
I just couldn't imagine
why anybody would watch it.

47:45.766 --> 47:48.900 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
