said, "Hey, baby, love your

48:39.000 --> 48:40.000 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
show."

48:40.000 --> 48:41.200 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
(LAUGHTER)

48:41.200 --> 48:43.233 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
INA GARTEN: And I
thought, that's food.

48:43.233 --> 48:47.633 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
I think my cookbook audience
might be slightly different
from my TV audience, but I think

48:47.633 --> 48:49.966 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
they're people that
