48:49.966 --> 48:53.133 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
You're doing a beautiful
job, I have to tell you.

48:53.133 --> 48:54.233 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
WILLIAM BRANGHAM:
You're just saying that.

